'''线粒体融合'''是[[线粒体|线粒体]]之间相互合并的过程，在[[真核细胞|真核细胞]]持续进行并受到高度调控。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = H Sesaki, RE Jensen
 | title = Division versus fusion: Dnm1p and Fzo1p antagonistically regulate mitochondrial shape
 | journal = Journal of Cell Biology
 | volume = 147
 | issue = 4
 | pages = 699-706
 | doi = 
 | pmid = 10562274
 | pmc = 2156171
 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2156171/
 | language = en |date=Nov 15, 1999}}</ref>线粒体融合对线粒体正常功能的发挥具有非常重要的作用。在融合过程中，线粒体之间可以进行[[线粒体DNA|线粒体DNA]]（mtDNA）的交换，以修复[[衰老|衰老]]和[[环境|环境]]因素导致的[[DNA损伤|DNA损伤]]或[[基因突变|基因突变]]。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = 漆正堂、丁树哲、贺杰
 | title = 线粒体融合蛋白Mitofusin在胰岛素抵抗发生与防治中的作用
 | journal = 生命科学
 | volume = 20
 | issue = 4
 | pages = 599-604
 | doi = 
 | url = http://so.med.wanfangdata.com.cn/ViewHTML/PeriodicalPaper_smkx200804015.aspx
 | language = zh |date=Apr 2008}}</ref>[[人类|人类]]细胞需要通过线粒体融合的互补作用来抵抗衰老；[[酵母菌|酵母菌]]细胞线粒体融合发生障碍会引起呼吸链缺陷。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Westermann B
 | title = Merging mitochondria matters: cellular role and molecular machinery of mitochondrial fusion
 | journal = EMBO Reports
 | volume = 3
 | issue = 6
 | pages = 527-531
 | issn = 1469221X
 | doi = 10.1093/embo-reports/kvf113
 | pmid = 12052774
 | pmc = 1084147
 | url = http://www.mendeley.com/research/merging-mitochondria-matters-cellular-role-molecular-machinery-mitochondrial-fusion-1/
 | language = en
 | date = Jun 2002
 | access-date = 2011-09-04
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111215135655/http://www.mendeley.com/research/merging-mitochondria-matters-cellular-role-molecular-machinery-mitochondrial-fusion-1/
 | archive-date = 2011-12-15
 | dead-url = yes
 }}</ref>线粒体间的融合需在一种分子量约为800kDa的蛋白质[[复合物|复合物]]——“[[融合装置|融合装置]]”（fision machinery）的介导下进行，<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Westermann B
 | title = Molecular machinery of mitochondrial fusion and fission
 | journal = Journal of Biological Chemistry
 | volume = 283
 | issue = 20
 | pages = 13501-13505 
 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.R800011200
 | pmid = 18372247
 | url = http://www.jbc.org/content/283/20/13501.full.pdf
 | language = en |date=Mar 27, 2008}}</ref>该过程可大致分为四个步骤：锚定、[[线粒体外膜|外膜]]融合、[[线粒体内膜|内膜]]融合以及[[线粒体基质|基质]]内含物融合。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = 耿红、孟紫强
 | title = 线粒体融合机制研究进展
 | journal = 细胞生物学杂志
 | year = 2003
 | month = 
 | volume = 25
 | issue = 1
 | pages = 17-21 
 | doi = 
 | url = http://so.med.wanfangdata.com.cn/ViewHTML/PeriodicalPaper_xbswxzz200301005.aspx
 | language = zh }}</ref>

线粒体融合与[[线粒体分裂|线粒体分裂]]一般保持[[动态平衡|动态平衡]]，<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Chen H, Chan DC
 | title = Mitochondrial dynamics in mammals
 | journal = Current Topics in Developmental Biology
 | year = 2004
 | month = 
 | volume = 59
 | issue = 
 | pages = 119-144
 | pmid = 14975249
 | url = http://www.its.caltech.edu/~chanlab/PDFs/Chen_Chan_CTD.pdf
 | language = en }}</ref>这种平衡对维持线粒体正常的形态、分布和功能十分重要。融合异常会导致线粒体形态延长，进而影响线粒体的功能。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Diaz F, Moraes CT
 | title = Mitochondrial biogenesis and turnover
 | journal = Cell Calcium
 | volume = 44
 | issue = 1
 | pages = 24-35
 | pmid = 18395251
 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18395251
 | language = en |date=Jul 2008}}</ref>融合活动异常的线粒体[[膜电位|膜电位]]通常会降低，并最终经线粒体[[自噬作用|自噬作用]]清除。

